Nordex Gains in Frankfurt on Retraction of Wind Energy Aid Cut

-- B y   J u l i e   C r u z
-- 
2011-06-06T07:25:52Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-06/nordex-gains-in-frankfurt-on-retraction-of-wind-energy-aid-cut.html
Nordex SE (NDX1)  rose as much as 7 percent
in  Frankfurt  as  Germany ’s BDEW utilities association said it
welcomes a plan by the government to retract a “significant”
reduction in subsidies paid to the operators of wind turbines on
land.   Shares of the wind-turbine maker gained 4.6 percent to 6.94
euros as of 9:22 a.m. local time.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Julie Cruz at 
 jcruz6@bloomberg.net  